<Base
  title="How to Find Brands That Already Sponsor Creators Like You"
  description="The highest-converting sponsor prospect is a brand already paying creators in your niche: they have budget, a process, and proof the channel works. The reverse-prospecting workflow — mine competitor sponsors, ad libraries, and niche directories."
